[FILE:362:descriptions/desc.single]
Libwps is a library (for use by word procesors, for example) for importing
the Microsoft Works word processor file format. It imports Works format
versions 2, 3, 4, 5 (aka 2000), and 8 with some formatting. The scope of
this project is just a Works word processor import filter, so there are no
plans for supporting an export filter, spreadsheets, or databases.


